                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">
                        Plugins with Lua
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                    No Virtual DOM overhead. Sandboxed execution with nanosecond
                    cold-start times. Perfect for high-throughput plugin hooks.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-6">
                    <span
                        class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide border bg-orange-900/10 border-orange-500/20 text-orange-400"
                    >
                        Sandboxed
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="md:col-span-12 p-8 rounded-xl bg-vayload-bg-card border border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-colors vayload-card flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-full bg-blue-900/5 blur-[100px] group-hover:bg-blue-600/10 transition-all duration-700"
            >
            </div>

            <div class="md:w-1/2 relative z-10">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-blue-900/20 text-blue-500">
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="28"
                            height="28"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                        >
                            <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline>
                            <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">
                        Why Lua over JavaScript?
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
                    We chose Lua to avoid the memory overhead of V8 or QuickJS.
                    LuaJIT offers <span class="text-white">C-like speeds</span> with
                    negligible cold-start times, making it perfect for high-throughput
                    plugin hooks in a Go environment.
                </p>
                <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                    <span
                        class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide border bg-blue-900/10 border-blue-500/20 text-blue-400"
                    >
                        Nanosecond Cold Start
                    </span>
                    <span
                        class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide border bg-blue-900/10 border-blue-500/20 text-blue-400"
                    >
                        Safe Sandboxing
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="md:w-1/2 w-full bg-vayload-bg rounded-lg border border-white/10 p-4 font-mono text-sm relative shadow-2xl"
            >
                <div
                    class="text-neutral-500 mb-2 border-b border-white/5 pb-2 flex justify-between"
                >
                    <span>hook_benchmark.log</span>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-xs font-mono">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class="text-neutral-400 w-24">NodeJS / V8</span>
                        <div
                            class="flex-1 h-2 bg-red-900/30 rounded-full overflow-hidden mx-4"
                        >
                            <div class="w-[80%] h-full bg-red-500"></div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-red-400 w-12 text-right">45ms</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class="text-neutral-400 w-24">QuickJS</span>
                        <div
                            class="flex-1 h-2 bg-yellow-900/30 rounded-full overflow-hidden mx-4"
                        >
                            <div class="w-[40%] h-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-yellow-400 w-12 text-right">12ms</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                        <span class="text-white font-bold w-24"
                            >Vayload (Lua)</span
                        >
                        <div
                            class="flex-1 h-2 bg-blue-900/30 rounded-full overflow-hidden mx-4"
                        >
                            <div class="w-[5%] h-full bg-blue-500"></div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-blue-400 w-12 text-right"
                            >&lt;1ms</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
